The pill I just

291
00:11:35,879 --> 00:11:37,159
swallowed

292
00:11:37,799 --> 00:11:40,960
is called the Honest-and-True-Word-of-Honor Pill.

293
00:11:41,159 --> 00:11:42,120
Once you take this pill,

294
00:11:42,159 --> 00:11:43,360
you must answer every question,

295
00:11:43,399 --> 00:11:45,159
and only speak the truth.

296
00:11:45,399 --> 00:11:48,600
That name sounds totally made up.

297
00:11:49,799 --> 00:11:50,960
It's not made up.

298
00:11:51,240 --> 00:11:52,919
I took this pill when I was little.

299
00:11:53,399 --> 00:11:55,960
Back then, Royal Brother used me as his test subject.

300
00:12:14,919 --> 00:12:16,320
Have you been studying hard?

301
00:12:16,600 --> 00:12:18,960
I wasn't studying. I was drawing comics.

302
00:12:24,559 --> 00:12:25,600
Don't believe me?

303
00:12:26,600 --> 00:12:27,600
Try it yourself.

304
00:12:30,279 --> 00:12:31,080
I won't take it.

305
00:12:31,360 --> 00:12:33,360
Who knows if your pill is poisoned?

306
00:12:33,519 --> 00:12:34,320
Down it goes!

307
00:12:35,000 --> 00:12:36,360
Hey, hey! Are you crazy?

308
00:12:36,600 --> 00:12:37,279
It's fine.

309
00:12:37,279 --> 00:12:38,440
I trust Prince Chengle's character.

310
00:12:38,440 --> 00:12:39,600
The Crown Prince said it's fine.

311
00:12:40,799 --> 00:12:42,080
Thank you, Envoy.

312
00:12:43,519 --> 00:12:45,120
Let me ask you.

313
00:12:45,360 --> 00:12:46,919
In this whole world,

314
00:12:47,120 --> 00:12:49,960
what matters the most?

315
00:12:52,000 --> 00:12:53,559
Talk nonsense again and you'll regret it.

316
00:12:53,559 --> 00:12:54,399
Huahua matters the most!

317
00:12:56,919 --> 00:12:58,039
You're playing along with him?

318
00:12:58,360 --> 00:12:58,919
No, no, it's just...

319
00:12:59,360 --> 00:13:01,399
My mouth moved on its own, I couldn't control it.

320
00:13:01,639 --> 00:13:02,600
Now you believe me, right?

321
00:13:02,600 --> 00:13:03,960
I couldn't control what came out.

322
00:13:04,240 --> 00:13:05,840
If it's really true,

323
00:13:06,399 --> 00:13:08,399
ask me, ask me, ask me!

324
00:13:10,919 --> 00:13:12,080
Am I pretty?

325
00:13:12,360 --> 00:13:14,559
That question shows no self-awareness at all.

326
00:13:15,159 --> 00:13:15,840
You!

327
00:13:16,120 --> 00:13:18,039
I have a Longevity Pill at my mansion.

328
00:13:18,120 --> 00:13:19,360
If we can get it,

329
00:13:19,919 --> 00:13:21,639
then, then, then...

330
00:13:22,159 --> 00:13:23,039
the truth will come out!

331
00:13:23,320 --> 00:13:24,000
Fine.

332
00:13:24,960 --> 00:13:26,799
Then let's go to your mansion to get it.

333
00:13:31,480 --> 00:13:33,120
Once I take this 100% Luck Pill,

334
00:13:33,679 --> 00:13:36,200
I'll surely defeat Qi Zhi and seize the throne.

335
00:13:37,159 --> 00:13:38,039
Doctor.

336
00:13:38,440 --> 00:13:39,039
I'm sick.

337
00:13:39,240 --> 00:13:40,440
I have a very strange illness.

338
00:13:43,559 --> 00:13:45,559
No matter what I do,

339
00:13:45,720 --> 00:13:47,039
I always end up failing.

340
00:13:47,759 --> 00:13:50,399
Is there a cure for this?

341
00:13:50,759 --> 00:13:51,559
One moment.

342
00:14:09,240 --> 00:14:10,799
This is called the 100% Luck Pill.

343
00:14:11,240 --> 00:14:16,399
Take it and everything will go smoothly.

344
00:14:29,960 --> 00:14:31,519
Do not take it at night.

345
00:14:32,440 --> 00:14:34,759
Otherwise, you'll get cramps and diarrhea.

346
00:14:35,759 --> 00:14:37,159
Always glad to help.

347
00:14:45,799 --> 00:14:48,480
Just two people? Easy to handle.

348
00:14:48,759 --> 00:14:50,840
But helping you comes with conditions.

349
00:14:51,120 --> 00:14:52,519
You're bringing this up now?

350
00:14:52,799 --> 00:14:53,799
Get used to it.

351
00:14:55,600 --> 00:14:56,399
One.

352
00:14:57,960 --> 00:15:00,679
After this is over, you must return to the palace with us and be Emperor.

353
00:15:00,799 --> 00:15:02,879
And make me your Empress.

354
00:15:03,320 --> 00:15:05,039
Even if I marry you, I'll banish you to the cold palace.

355
00:15:07,600 --> 00:15:09,200
Fine, I agree.

356
00:15:09,600 --> 00:15:10,559
I'll return to the palace with you,

357
00:15:10,759 --> 00:15:11,840
marry you as Empress,

358
00:15:11,919 --> 00:15:13,399
and won't banish you to the cold palace.

359
00:15:13,799 --> 00:15:14,600
Good.

360
00:15:14,600 --> 00:15:15,320
Two.

361
00:15:15,360 --> 00:15:17,360
We will never share a bed.

362
00:15:17,559 --> 00:15:18,519
Couldn't ask for anything better.

363
00:15:19,000 --> 00:15:19,639
Three.

364
00:15:19,639 --> 00:15:23,519
Never touch those phony hocus-pocus things again.

365
00:15:23,600 --> 00:15:27,399
No more deceiving people, no more touching those pills.

366
00:15:30,759 --> 00:15:32,919
I am Daliang's Modern Shennong!

367
00:15:33,799 --> 00:15:35,399
When has anyone taken my pills and found them useless?

368
00:15:36,399 --> 00:15:37,039
That...

369
00:15:37,240 --> 00:15:38,240
that kid...

370
00:15:38,799 --> 00:15:40,440
that kid was just an accident.

371
00:15:41,759 --> 00:15:43,360
How can you say I'm a phony?

372
00:15:43,600 --> 00:15:44,399
You're just biased against me.

373
00:15:44,440 --> 00:15:45,399
Cut the nonsense.

374
00:15:46,080 --> 00:15:48,600
Just say if you agree or not.

375
00:15:55,799 --> 00:15:57,559
I agree. I'll never touch pills again.

376
00:16:14,480 --> 00:16:15,039
Let's go.

377
00:16:15,200 --> 00:16:15,799
Let's go check it out.

378
00:16:16,799 --> 00:16:18,519
This routine feels so familiar.

379
00:16:44,799 --> 00:16:45,600
Oh.

380
00:16:45,960 --> 00:16:49,039
Your Longevity Pill wasn't confiscated?

381
00:16:51,159 --> 00:16:52,440
Of course not.

382
00:16:53,840 --> 00:16:57,159
I disguised the Longevity Pill as a pink pearl.

383
00:16:57,919 --> 00:16:59,440
And strung it on a gold chain.

384
00:16:59,960 --> 00:17:00,960
Hidden like that,

385
00:17:00,960 --> 00:17:02,320
how could anyone possibly find it?

386
00:17:03,000 --> 00:17:04,799
You hid it in such a discreet spot,

387
00:17:04,799 --> 00:17:06,920
no one would find it even without a disguise.

388
00:17:07,519 --> 00:17:08,920
Even without a disguise,

389
00:17:09,160 --> 00:17:11,599
a pink pearl on a huge gold chain

390
00:17:11,759 --> 00:17:12,960
is pretty flashy, don't you think?

391
00:17:18,599 --> 00:17:19,599
Who's over there?

392
00:17:21,119 --> 00:17:21,920
Uh...

393
00:17:22,599 --> 00:17:25,319
The Crown Prince, Prince Chengle, Ouyang Yan, and dashing Qi Zhi are inside.

394
00:17:27,039 --> 00:17:27,960
What are you guys doing?

395
00:17:27,960 --> 00:17:29,519
Looking for the Longevity Pill, but no luck.

396
00:17:29,720 --> 00:17:30,400
Oh, come on!

397
00:17:30,400 --> 00:17:30,960
Are you out of your mind?

398
00:17:30,960 --> 00:17:31,640
Go, go, go! Hurry up!

399
00:17:31,640 --> 00:17:32,160
Guards!

400
00:17:32,440 --> 00:17:33,200
Someone's inside!

401
00:17:33,599 --> 00:17:34,599
Catch the thieves!

402
00:17:35,200 --> 00:17:36,319
Somebody, hurry!

403
00:17:37,440 --> 00:17:39,200
We escaped through the second window on the west side!

404
00:17:39,400 --> 00:17:40,240
You, Qi!

405
00:17:44,880 --> 00:17:45,720
Ouch!

406
00:17:46,799 --> 00:17:47,279
Shh!

407
00:17:47,599 --> 00:17:48,519
Shh!

408
00:17:48,599 --> 00:17:50,240
How am I supposed to control myself?

409
00:17:50,640 --> 00:17:51,640
In my experience,

410
00:17:51,640 --> 00:17:53,359
just shut up whenever you can.

411
00:17:54,000 --> 00:17:56,160
Now your Longevity Pill is gone.

412
00:17:56,240 --> 00:17:57,599
How are you supposed to prove your innocence?

413
00:17:59,319 --> 00:18:00,359
I just remembered!

414
00:18:01,039 --> 00:18:01,799
One time,

415
00:18:02,480 --> 00:18:03,799
after I took the Melancholy Pill,

416
00:18:04,599 --> 00:18:05,400
I got all worked up

417
00:18:06,240 --> 00:18:08,759
and gave that necklace to one of my concubines.

418
00:18:09,680 --> 00:18:10,799
Which concubine?

419
00:18:14,160 --> 00:18:16,559
We used to party together all the time.

420
00:18:19,240 --> 00:18:21,480
Looking back now, I really miss those days.

421
00:18:40,720 --> 00:18:42,400
You want a "Big Sword" service?

422
00:18:45,240 --> 00:18:46,319
I won't lie to you, miss,

423
00:18:47,359 --> 00:18:48,799
but with your looks, doing that kind of work

424
00:18:49,200 --> 00:18:51,640
doesn't seem too suitable.

425
00:18:52,759 --> 00:18:53,559
How vulgar!

426
00:18:54,599 --> 00:18:55,400
My dear!

427
00:18:57,559 --> 00:18:58,359
Aha!

428
00:18:59,200 --> 00:19:00,000
Prince!

429
00:19:00,200 --> 00:19:01,000
Hey...

430
00:19:03,839 --> 00:19:06,480
This scene is so jarring. No aesthetic at all.

431
00:19:06,559 --> 00:19:07,279
Shh!

432
00:19:07,400 --> 00:19:09,119
My Prince,

433
00:19:09,119 --> 00:19:11,480
I've missed you so much.

434
00:19:12,119 --> 00:19:13,960
How have you been lately?

435
00:19:14,559 --> 00:19:16,839
You look so thin and starved.

436
00:19:18,640 --> 00:19:22,440
Did you risk coming to see me because you missed me?

437
00:19:24,240 --> 00:19:25,359
Of course.

438
00:19:25,799 --> 00:19:27,960
Day and night, I longed to be with you...

439
00:19:27,960 --> 00:19:29,759
Cut it out. He didn't miss you at all. He just—

440
00:19:31,640 --> 00:19:33,319
Keep your mouth shut!

441
00:19:33,319 --> 00:19:34,799
Of course it was

442
00:19:35,440 --> 00:19:36,680
to see you.

443
00:19:39,960 --> 00:19:41,720
Even if I never see you again,

444
00:19:42,599 --> 00:19:43,720
my heart

445
00:19:44,559 --> 00:19:45,640
will be at peace.

446
00:19:46,119 --> 00:19:48,400
Yeah right. He's only at peace 'cause of your necklace.

447
00:19:51,000 --> 00:19:51,799
Necklace?

448
00:19:53,039 --> 00:19:53,839
Why?

449
00:19:54,799 --> 00:19:55,599
My dear,

450
00:19:56,400 --> 00:19:57,519
do you remember

451
00:19:58,240 --> 00:19:59,960
when you and I

452
00:20:00,200 --> 00:20:01,599
danced with swords and sang songs?

453
00:20:02,119 --> 00:20:03,839
Such happy times!

454
00:20:04,640 --> 00:20:05,720
I remember, I remember.

455
00:20:06,319 --> 00:20:09,200
That day you insisted on giving me this necklace.

456
00:20:09,799 --> 00:20:11,119
I was so happy.

457
00:20:12,559 --> 00:20:14,720
That's 'cause he took a Melancholy Pill before giving you that thing.

458
00:20:14,720 --> 00:20:16,559
He wasn't sincere with you at all—

459
00:20:17,880 --> 00:20:18,799
Really?

460
00:20:19,200 --> 00:20:20,400
Of course not!

461
00:20:20,559 --> 00:20:21,200
Hey,

462
00:20:21,480 --> 00:20:23,039
Didn't you take the Truth Pill? Why aren't you telling the truth?

463
00:20:23,039 --> 00:20:24,960
You idiot. He made the pill, so he knows the antidote.

464
00:20:25,960 --> 00:20:26,799
Shut up!

465
00:20:27,359 --> 00:20:29,119
Ugh, both of you, shut up!

466
00:20:30,200 --> 00:20:30,920
I need to go relieve myself.

467
00:20:31,039 --> 00:20:31,599
Then I—

468
00:20:31,599 --> 00:20:33,119
I don't need to go!

469
00:20:36,359 --> 00:20:36,920
My dear,

470
00:20:37,839 --> 00:20:39,079
my sincere feelings for you

471
00:20:39,200 --> 00:20:40,680
are clear as day.

472
00:20:41,839 --> 00:20:42,400
You...

473
00:20:42,680 --> 00:20:44,440
Don't you believe me?

474
00:20:47,960 --> 00:20:52,119
Time to taste Liu Heng's secret Bewitching Incense!

475
00:20:55,880 --> 00:20:57,039
Little Twenty-Eight!

476
00:20:57,160 --> 00:20:59,400
What are you doing here?

477
00:21:06,000 --> 00:21:07,599
Are you alright?

478
00:21:08,519 --> 00:21:09,720
Just helping out.

479
00:21:11,000 --> 00:21:12,440
This is agony!

480
00:21:14,000 --> 00:21:15,640
Then tell me,

481
00:21:15,839 --> 00:21:18,200
did you come here today to take back this necklace?

482
00:21:18,519 --> 00:21:20,200
Of course not.

483
00:21:21,960 --> 00:21:25,960
I came to do some maintenance on it.

484
00:21:25,960 --> 00:21:27,200
Look at this pearl.

485
00:21:27,519 --> 00:21:30,640
It's already worn thin here.

486
00:21:30,759 --> 00:21:32,119
Of course it's thin.

487
00:21:32,400 --> 00:21:33,920
Because this pearl is a fake!

488
00:21:36,240 --> 00:21:37,039
You...

489
00:21:39,759 --> 00:21:42,640
No wonder when I showed it to my sisters,

490
00:21:43,200 --> 00:21:45,000
they all laughed at me.

491
00:21:45,799 --> 00:21:47,039
You deceived me!

492
00:21:47,359 --> 00:21:48,400
My dear!

493
00:21:49,519 --> 00:21:50,400
My dear!

494
00:21:50,960 --> 00:21:52,839
Listen to me.

495
00:21:53,119 --> 00:21:54,319
You'd better listen to me.

496
00:21:54,400 --> 00:21:55,960
That pearl was a fake to begin with.

497
00:21:56,000 --> 00:21:57,000
It's actually a pill.

498
00:21:57,000 --> 00:21:58,480
And this pill can prove his innocence.

499
00:21:58,839 --> 00:22:00,960
That's why he came to you. Otherwise he wouldn't have thought of you at all.

500
00:22:06,160 --> 00:22:07,880
You mean...

501
00:22:08,119 --> 00:22:09,440
this can save him?

502
00:22:09,799 --> 00:22:10,599
Exactly.

503
00:22:12,559 --> 00:22:14,039
Without this necklace,

504
00:22:14,519 --> 00:22:15,519
he's a dead man.

505
00:22:15,720 --> 00:22:17,039
She's absolutely right!

506
00:22:19,400 --> 00:22:20,839
You heartless jerk!

507
00:22:27,960 --> 00:22:29,440
The pill that can save me!

508
00:22:31,839 --> 00:22:33,480
Wow!

509
00:22:38,680 --> 00:22:39,240
Hurry!

510
00:22:39,480 --> 00:22:41,079
Take the pills to Ascension Hall!

511
00:22:43,240 --> 00:22:44,920
This is all your fault!

512
00:22:45,200 --> 00:22:47,440
You made me take that hair-growth pill.

513
00:22:47,680 --> 00:22:49,400
That's why I look like a man now!

514
00:22:49,799 --> 00:22:50,759
It's all your fault!

515
00:22:51,119 --> 00:22:52,400
My dear!

516
00:22:56,559 --> 00:22:58,160
Prince Chengle didn't come back all night.

517
00:22:58,160 --> 00:22:59,640
Your trip here was quite the adventure.

518
00:23:00,319 --> 00:23:01,319
There are so many princes,

519
00:23:01,319 --> 00:23:03,240
yet you had to pick this phony prince.

520
00:23:03,400 --> 00:23:04,519
Look at all the trouble it caused.

521
00:23:04,720 --> 00:23:07,240
This is nothing. You haven't seen anything yet.

522
00:23:08,400 --> 00:23:09,359
How dare you ignore me!

523
00:23:09,440 --> 00:23:11,480
Can you give me a break?

524
00:23:11,799 --> 00:23:13,319
You don't need a break talking to him,

525
00:23:13,400 --> 00:23:14,640
but you do when talking to me?

526
00:23:14,799 --> 00:23:15,720
What's that supposed to mean?

527
00:23:15,720 --> 00:23:16,799
I was answering his question.

528
00:23:16,799 --> 00:23:18,000
You didn't ask me anything.

529
00:23:18,200 --> 00:23:19,319
Fine, now I'm asking. What did you mean?

530
00:23:19,480 --> 00:23:20,480
I didn't mean anything.

531
00:23:21,000 --> 00:23:22,640
This isn't the time to argue.

532
00:23:22,720 --> 00:23:23,039
Exactly.

533
00:23:23,079 --> 00:23:24,200
Who's arguing with him?

534
00:23:24,240 --> 00:23:26,279
Oh, not arguing? Then why so loud?

535
00:23:26,400 --> 00:23:27,440
Loud? You're being ridiculous.

536
00:23:27,720 --> 00:23:29,000
You dare say I'm loud?

537
00:23:29,119 --> 00:23:30,039
You got a death wish?

538
00:23:30,200 --> 00:23:31,799
Something feels off here.

539
00:23:31,799 --> 00:23:32,359
Huh?

540
00:23:32,359 --> 00:23:33,920
Hey, a patient's coming.

541
00:23:33,920 --> 00:23:35,200
Doctor, I need treatment!

542
00:23:35,319 --> 00:23:36,799
Please, examine me quickly!

543
00:23:41,279 --> 00:23:41,839
Doctor.

544
00:23:42,559 --> 00:23:43,920
I followed your prescription,

545
00:23:43,920 --> 00:23:45,359
so why haven't I lost weight?

546
00:23:50,119 --> 00:23:50,920
Last night, you ate

547
00:23:51,000 --> 00:23:52,519
five drumsticks, eight buns, seven trays of dumplings,

548
00:23:52,559 --> 00:23:53,680
and a bowl of malatang. You still want to slim down?

549
00:23:53,839 --> 00:23:54,960
You're dreaming!

550
00:23:55,400 --> 00:23:56,000
Hmph!

551
00:24:03,359 --> 00:24:03,920
Doctor!

552
00:24:04,200 --> 00:24:05,720
We gave him your medicine,

553
00:24:06,039 --> 00:24:08,240
but our child is still so naughty!

554
00:24:13,519 --> 00:24:14,519
You parents

555
00:24:14,640 --> 00:24:15,960
never bother to discipline your kids

556
00:24:15,960 --> 00:24:17,039
or spend time playing with them.

557
00:24:17,200 --> 00:24:18,559
Then when their behavior goes wrong,

558
00:24:18,559 --> 00:24:19,799
you try to fix it with pills.

559
00:24:19,799 --> 00:24:20,720
Take a look at yourselves first.

560
00:24:20,720 --> 00:24:21,799
Are you fit to be parents?

561
00:24:22,960 --> 00:24:23,799
Let's go.

562
00:24:30,119 --> 00:24:31,359
Goodness, chicken-raiser!

563
00:24:32,200 --> 00:24:33,200
You now have both

564
00:24:33,480 --> 00:24:36,039
mind-reading and 100% truth-telling powers.

565
00:24:36,400 --> 00:24:38,799
You're a walking time bomb!

566
00:24:49,920 --> 00:24:50,559
Doctor.

567
00:24:51,720 --> 00:24:53,799
My child was taken and is missing.

568
00:24:55,200 --> 00:24:56,400
My heart is in agony.

569
00:24:56,960 --> 00:24:59,519
Please give me something for this heartache.

570
00:25:01,000 --> 00:25:02,000
Don't tell me

571
00:25:02,799 --> 00:25:05,160
you're a parent of a child harmed by Prince Chengle?

572
00:25:07,880 --> 00:25:09,160
Doctor, your insight is astounding.

573
00:25:13,519 --> 00:25:15,359
So it seems this is really true.

574
00:25:17,440 --> 00:25:18,799
I miss my child so much.

575
00:25:19,359 --> 00:25:20,799
I don't know how to bear it.

576
00:25:21,440 --> 00:25:22,400
Even after all that's happened,

577
00:25:22,400 --> 00:25:23,799
you still believe in so-called miracle pills?

578
00:25:24,200 --> 00:25:25,200
Let me tell you,

579
00:25:25,319 --> 00:25:26,759
every miracle pill sold here

580
00:25:27,039 --> 00:25:28,519
is nothing but ordinary herbs.

581
00:25:43,200 --> 00:25:44,039
What's going on?

582
00:25:45,000 --> 00:25:45,599
Who is this?

583
00:25:45,599 --> 00:25:47,200
When you people run into trouble,

584
00:25:47,559 --> 00:25:49,200
you don't try to solve it, you just avoid it.

585
00:25:50,160 --> 00:25:52,960
You hope some miracle pill will save you.

586
00:25:53,559 --> 00:25:54,880
But you don't realize, in this world,

587
00:25:54,880 --> 00:25:56,400
no such medicine exists.

588
00:25:56,519 --> 00:25:58,000
You're just being cheated for nothing.

589
00:26:09,519 --> 00:26:10,640
You're all here.

590
00:26:10,640 --> 00:26:11,200
Let's...

591
00:26:14,960 --> 00:26:15,799
Run!

592
00:26:15,799 --> 00:26:16,759
Hey, split up!

593
00:26:16,759 --> 00:26:17,319
Hurry, hurry!

594
00:26:17,319 --> 00:26:18,039
Hey, hey!

595
00:26:18,039 --> 00:26:18,680
Ouyang Yan!

596
00:26:18,680 --> 00:26:19,519
I'm here, I'm here!

597
00:26:22,960 --> 00:26:23,799
After them!

598
00:26:30,319 --> 00:26:31,839
Hurry! Don't let them escape!

599
00:26:31,839 --> 00:26:32,640
This way!

600
00:26:35,920 --> 00:26:36,799
Halt!

601
00:26:37,200 --> 00:26:37,960
Stop running!

602
00:26:42,640 --> 00:26:43,319
Quick, quick!

603
00:26:43,319 --> 00:26:43,839
Hey.

604
00:26:43,839 --> 00:26:44,599
They're hunting you everywhere now.

605
00:26:44,920 --> 00:26:45,720
Why not come over to my side?

606
00:26:45,720 --> 00:26:46,279
Move aside!

607
00:26:46,599 --> 00:26:47,359
Don't make me hurt you.

608
00:26:49,000 --> 00:26:49,880
Hide, quick!

609
00:26:57,599 --> 00:26:58,400
At the crucial moment,

610
00:26:58,599 --> 00:26:59,920
brothers are the most reliable!

611
00:26:59,960 --> 00:27:00,960
Go, all of you, hurry!

612
00:27:01,359 --> 00:27:02,519
Did you take the wrong pill or what?

613
00:27:03,720 --> 00:27:04,519
Farewell!

614
00:27:09,160 --> 00:27:09,839
This pill's effect...

615
00:27:10,200 --> 00:27:11,759
This pill is way too potent!

616
00:27:12,599 --> 00:27:13,400
Whoa.

617
00:27:14,720 --> 00:27:15,279
Over there!

618
00:27:15,440 --> 00:27:16,559
I know a road out of the city.

619
00:27:16,559 --> 00:27:17,519
Hey, wait.

620
00:27:18,359 --> 00:27:20,240
Prince, didn't you say once we hand the pills over,

621
00:27:20,240 --> 00:27:21,519
it would prove your innocence?

622
00:27:21,559 --> 00:27:22,720
So why are you running now?

623
00:27:22,720 --> 00:27:24,920
Are you really that clueless?

624
00:27:25,440 --> 00:27:26,640
If the authorities cared about this,

625
00:27:26,960 --> 00:27:29,559
would I have ended up like this?

626
00:27:30,920 --> 00:27:31,480
They...

627
00:27:31,559 --> 00:27:35,039
They already think the pills are mumbo-jumbo.

628
00:27:35,480 --> 00:27:36,160
So,

629
00:27:36,839 --> 00:27:37,920
even if I hand the pills over,

630
00:27:38,240 --> 00:27:39,400
do you think they'd believe me?

631
00:27:40,559 --> 00:27:41,799
You're still lying to me.

632
00:27:42,599 --> 00:27:44,000
This isn't called lying.

633
00:27:44,160 --> 00:27:46,200
It's an expedient measure.

634
00:27:47,200 --> 00:27:48,559
Everyone who bought pills at Ascension Hall,

635
00:27:49,000 --> 00:27:49,799
your concubine,

636
00:27:49,960 --> 00:27:51,440
and the women who lost their children,

637
00:27:51,559 --> 00:27:52,599
they were all deceived by you,

638
00:27:52,759 --> 00:27:54,400
harmed by your pills.

639
00:27:57,759 --> 00:27:58,799
I never deceived anyone.

640
00:27:59,680 --> 00:28:00,240
However,

641
00:28:00,960 --> 00:28:02,200
not every pill works, right?

642
00:28:03,799 --> 00:28:04,759
For medicine to progress,

643
00:28:05,200 --> 00:28:06,640
sacrifices must be made.

644
00:28:06,960 --> 00:28:07,559
Isn't that right?

645
00:28:08,960 --> 00:28:10,799
You've read my medical books.

646
00:28:11,119 --> 00:28:12,960
You understand me, don't you?

647
00:28:14,400 --> 00:28:15,400
You're my kindred spirit,

648
00:28:15,559 --> 00:28:16,240
aren't you?

649
00:28:16,480 --> 00:28:17,039
No.

650
00:28:19,039 --> 00:28:21,960
I can't judge your character based on your medical books alone.

651
00:28:23,559 --> 00:28:25,519
Talent and integrity are not the same thing.

652
00:28:26,920 --> 00:28:27,720
Guards!

653
00:28:28,000 --> 00:28:29,400
Prince Chengle and his accomplice are here!

654
00:28:29,400 --> 00:28:30,319
Come arrest me!

655
00:28:30,319 --> 00:28:31,559
You've gone mad! Hurry up and go!

656
00:28:31,559 --> 00:28:33,039
If you're a criminal, then I'm your accomplice.

657
00:28:33,039 --> 00:28:34,319
We deserve what we get.
